  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients presenting for elective surgery requiring orotracheal intubation will be randomized
      to being intubated with either the GlideScope Groove video-laryngoscope or the standard
      GlideScope video-laryngoscope.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      See above. The primary outcome is time to intubation.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
